<TEXT>
<P>
I was shocked when I read one of your viewers' comments on the Dec. 18 episode 
of "Newhart." 
</P>
<P>
Talk about a viewer completely missing the point of the show! The viewer 
ridiculed the show, claiming that it poked fun at an overweight woman. The 
woman was not overweight! She had a perfect figure except for a large derriere. 
The show highlighted how superficial people can be, judging each other on 
physical traits. Your viewer asked "Whatever happened to intelligent writers?" 
I ask "Whatever happened to intelligent viewers?" 
</P>
<P>
Sue Menn, Alhambra 
</P>
