<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONTROL FREAKS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding control freaks ("Who's the Boss?" by Margo Kaufman, Dec. 3): Power 
trips belong to a dying paradigm. A win-win partnership model is emerging in 
fields as broad as world politics and as close as our own families. To reduce 
the number of future control freaks, we should be raising children with 
respect, learning how to share decision making with our partners and families 
and taking better care of ourselves and our own self-esteem. 
</P>
<P>
JAELLINE JAFFE, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
