<HEADLINE>
<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"It was an emotional roller coaster for all of us. What was never supposed to 
happen to our system was actually happening right before our eyes." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Jim Nelson, manager of AT&amp;T's network operations facility, describing 
the effort to find the cause of last week's long-distance network breakdown. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
