<P>
Profession: Owner of metal-fabricating firm. 
</P>
<P>
Education: High school graduate, 3 1/2 years of college. 
</P>
<P>
Local commissions, service clubs, organizations: Member of YMCA Board of 
Managers, former member of board of directors of Chamber of Commerce, former 
president of Kiwanis Club, member of Elks Lodge. 
</P>
