<P>
'76 E. GERMAN NUCLEAR INCIDENT DESCRIBED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BONN 
</P>
