involved in politics and public service in Missouri, can see state capitol from 
his office. STEVE JONES; Photo, Joe and Joyce Cruzan of Carterville, Mo., at 
left, are waging legal battle to remove their brain-dead daughter from 
life-support systems. Right, Nancy Cruzan before the accident that left her 
comatose. MIKE GULLETT 
</P>
